commit.message:
Restrict "auto using *" and friends to global references.

This is in line with the documentation, which only mentions qualified
identifiers. The interpretation of terms is actually much trickier than
it seems since it also involves resolution of implicit arguments and
typeclasses. The code can be ported in a backwards compatible way by
pose-ing the corresponding "using" clauses before invoking auto.
